ADDITIONAL TERMS FOR RESEARCH USE

This software is designed for legitimate scientific research and documentation
of aerial phenomena. Users are responsible for:

1. Ensuring they have proper rights to analyze any video content
2. Respecting privacy laws and regulations in their jurisdiction  
3. Using the software ethically and responsibly
4. Properly attributing the software in research publications
5. Not using the software for surveillance or harmful purposes

The authors encourage open collaboration and sharing of findings within the
scientific community while respecting all applicable laws and ethical guidelines.